maya is a 2015 pakistani horror film which is directorial debut of jawad bashir and produced by hina jawad under production banner &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; films . the film features assembled cast including ahmed abdul rehman , hina jawad , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; afzal , sheikh mohammad ahmed and anam malik . hina jawad played the lead role of maya in film . the film 's story is inspired from a real paranormal event that occurred in denmark . the film was released nationwide on june 12 , 2015 .